    <text type="letter">    
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_vm.00397_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place"><handShift rend="printed"/>The Truth Seeker Company,</name>
                    <name type="place">Booksellers And Publishers,</name>
                    <name type="place">28 Lafayette Place.</name>
                    <name type="place">New York,</name>
                    <date when="1891-01-31"><handShift rend="manuscript"/><hi rend="underline">Jan 31</hi> <handShift rend="printed"/>189<handShift rend="manuscript"/>1</date>
                    <note type="editorial" resp="#ww">book sent by mail Feb:3</note>
                    </dateline>
                <salute>Dear Sir</salute> 
            </opener>
            <p>
                The Ingersoll<ptr target="n0839"/>&#8211;Field<ptr target="loc.04252_n1"/> Discussion<ptr target="loc.04252_n2"/> 
                is out of print in paper. We have copies
                in cloth&#8212;at 1<hi rend="underline">00</hi></p>
            <p>
                Will you please send to Wm. J. Nicolay, Minier, Ill.<ptr target="loc.04252_n3"/>
                1 <hi rend="underline">Complete Works</hi> of Walt Whitman<ptr target="n4195"/> 
                1 vol. Octavo, hf. cloth&#8212;</p>
            <p>McKay<ptr target="n4983"/> says this  book is owned
                by Mr Whitman &#38; that he can only give us 20&#37; on it.
                Hope you can do better&#8212;thro
                <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc_vm.00398_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
                 Mr Whitman, as this book is to be sold again, and we will 
                have to give Mr Nickolay a discount. Please send to him the cheapest
                way, &#38; send us bill.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Yours</salute>
                    <signed>Truth Seeker Co</signed>
                    <signed>B.</signed>
                </closer>
        </body> 
    </text> 
